            Summary
            Ambitious student pursuing a Bachelor of Science with Honours in Psychology. Skilled in statistics, mathematics, and psychological research methods, with great communication skills. Adaptable and driven with strong work ethic and ability to thrive in team-based or individually motivated settings
            
            
            Skills
            Strong mathematical aptitude.
            Data gathering and organization.
            Experience with JAMOVI, SPSS, and Excel.
            Communication skills, including written.
            Enthusiastic.
            Fast learner.
            Works well in a team, with strong leadership skills when needed.
            Decision making skills.
            Currently hold a full New Zealand drivers license and own a car.
            
            
            Education and Training
            Victoria University of Wellington
            Bachelor of Science Double Majoring in Mathematics and Psychology, 2018-202.
            Bachelor of Science with Honours Majoring in Psychology, 2021-Current.
            Hagley College
            High School Diploma, 2013-2017.
            
            
            Experience
            NumberWorks’nWords Kilbirnie
            Math Tutor, 2018-Current.
            Honey Café
            Barista, 2016-2018.
            PMP Distributors
            Paper Deliverer, 2013-2014.
